A video of the world map being played on a piano has received another jolt of love after it was reposted on social media. The original musical world map, created by John Keats, was posted last year and has amassed over 8-million views. His other videos, highlighting Russia, South America, America and Europe, have been equally popular.  In fact, here's his one dedicated solely to Africa: So it's no surprise others have jumped on to the bandwagon with their own versions. Our favourite one has to be the Africa remix, and the 492,000 users who liked @karaweeks_ tweet seem to agree as the tweet went viral last week. What do you you think?